# Keep the build context small and reproducible. The Dockerfile copies
# packages/shared, packages/server, packages/web and examples/ from the repo
# root, so those (and the SQL migrations under packages/server) are NOT ignored.
# Only build artifacts, VCS metadata, and test files are excluded.
.git
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
node_modules
**/node_modules
dist
**/dist
coverage
**/coverage
.turbo
**/.turbo
**/*.test.ts
